A vintage 1950s-style office scene with warm sepia tones, featuring a retro computer terminal with a glowing green screen displaying a friendly robotic face icon. In the foreground, an exhausted office worker in period-appropriate attire slumps dramatically over a wooden desk covered in scattered papers and an overflowing ashtray. The robot face on the screen appears sympathetic, with curved lines suggesting a gentle smile. On the wall behind, an ornate gilded frame contains an image of a sinking ship. The lighting is moody with dramatic shadows cast by a single desk lamp, creating a film noir atmosphere that contrasts the absurd humor of seeking emotional support from a machine.
